    "title_en": "First Observation of an Exotic Reggeon",
    "abstract_en": "We present new \\compass high-statistics measurements of the peripheral production of $ηπ^-$ and $η^\\prime π^-$ pairs in the reactions $π^- p \\to η^{(\\prime)}π^- p$. For the first time, we perform an unbinned analysis of the high-mass region of the $ηπ^-$ and $η^\\primeπ^-$ systems, which allows us to disentangle the exchange mechanisms governing their production. We report the first observation in high-energy scattering of an exotic Reggeon with high significance exceeding $5\\,σ$ for both channels, which is, most likely, related to the exotic $π_1(1600)$.8",
